For the first time in my career I am to embark on an ambitious solo pipe organ tour across Europe in November and December of this year, presenting my latest work, All Thoughts Fly on 17 different organs - dates and ticket info below. These beautiful organs all have different manuals and dispositions, they are big and small, old and new, and they live in different spaces, holy and unholy. I've had some technical requirements and it is impossible to create a tour like this without compromiseÂ butÂ that's also where the charm lies; some things are beyond my control, for better or worse. As a result each and every concert will be unique in terms of sound and volume. So, I hereby invite you to take part in this huge experiment of mine where I befriend these instruments for the first time and present "All thoughts fly" for organ and 12 speakers. Go to church, be embraced by the sound and let your thoughts fly. Endless amounts of gratitude to @giosalmoiraghi and @swampbooking for putting this tour together.
